 <title>Josephine</title>
 <link>https://vse.la/chris-rea/josephine</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;There&#039;s rain on my window&lt;br /&gt;
But I&#039;m thinking of you&lt;br /&gt;
Tears on my pillow&lt;br /&gt;
But I will come through&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;[Chorus]&lt;br /&gt;
Josephine, I&#039;ll send you all my love&lt;br /&gt;
And every single step I take&lt;br /&gt;
I take for you&lt;br /&gt;
Josephine&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There&#039;s a storm on my radar&lt;br /&gt;
But I can still fly&lt;br /&gt;
And you are the reason&lt;br /&gt;
The blue in my sky&lt;br /&gt;
Josephine&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A life without meaning&lt;br /&gt;
I was walking away&lt;br /&gt;
In the coldest of winters&lt;br /&gt;
Night becomes day&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(Chorus)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
